Former Lebanese Prime Minister Rafik Hariri was killed in a powerful explosion in central Beirut on Monday , Lebanese officials and medical sources said .On Monday , Hariri and eight other people were killed in a huge explosion , which occurred as Hariri 's motorcade was passing by in the seafront area of the Lebanese capital Beirut .But Hariri 's supporters have accused Syria and the Lebanese government of orchestrating the assassination .He was Rafik Hariri , a former and a future prime minister of Lebanon .